Detailed item info Product Information In the video game Alien: Isolation, pick up where the action from the science fiction horror classic movie ‘Alien’ left off and emerge yourself in this extra-terrestrial world. This video game takes place 15 years after the events of the sci-fi movie and puts you in control of Ellen Ripley’s daughter, Amanda Ripley. She is heading to the decommissioned space station Sevastopol to investigate her mother’s disappearance. However, not everything is as it seems as she notices an alien is loose in the space station and cannot be killed. In this first-person shooter, it is your job to make sure that Amanda and all of the humans make it out alive. There is also a separate game available called Survivor Mode. Each content in Survivor Mode features one-on-one battles that are timed.
